{"tid":1775693,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩所有檢測認証同路人入一入黎!!","createTime":"2019-12-09T04:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T08:34:04.000Z","uid":38055,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c224af6714eb83f0044a808d0a59fcaab744c274","tid":1775693,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"之前有幾個檢測証證post 好多同路人好活躍留言<br />\n對於各同路人大家都不停屌同行點點點。<br />\n而家我哋檢測認証界有屬於自己嘅第一個工會正式上線啦！<br />\n希望大家能夠多多支持，最好可以入會<br />\n就算唔入都可以發表下自己睇法，我哋會聽取你哋既意見去努力改善。請大家多多關照！<br />\n有任何問題都可以下面發問，我會盡力解答<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n‼️重大消息‼️<br />\n<br />\n🏛登記局刊憲確認我地工會既申請登記啦(進入正式審批程序)📖🎊🎉👏🏻👍🏻<br />\n距離工會正式成立 只差1⃣步‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n工會成立既過程已進入最後階段<br />\n🔬籌委會正積極籌備各類宣傳及內部行政事宜<br />\n<br />\n另外 工會已經開始接受會員申請🖋<br />\n快d加入啦!!✅<br />\n<br />\n入會資格：<br />\n凡通常居住在香港，並受僱於檢測及認證行業者(亦包括政府部門、各行各業的内部實驗室及品質管理部門)，即可申請。<br />\n<br />\n入會方式：<br />\nGoogle form: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/HKTCUEnroll\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKTCUEnroll&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=377d2d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/HKTCUEnroll</a><br />\n<br />\n聯絡：<br />\nFB Page: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/HKTCUFB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKTCUFB&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=628f1a83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/HKTCUFB</a><br />